{
  "texts": [
    "Effective research skills involve search, critical analysis, information synthesis, and communication of results.",
    "With advances in Artificial Intelligence (AI), tools like ChatGPT have emerged as potential resources to support these processes.",
    "This study explores how ChatGPT can be used to enhance investigative competencies in university students, a crucial aspect for their academic and professional success.In recent years, many educational institutions have recognized the importance of digital literacy and implemented continuous training programs for their teachers.",
    "These programs include modules on the use of digital technologies in research, management of bibliographic databases, and data analysis tools, aiming to keep teachers updated with new technologies and research methodologies [13].",
    "The availability of digital resources and online learning platforms has facilitated access to courses and educational materials on research skills, allowing teachers to learn and update their research techniques from anywhere."
  ]
}